@node LIBRARIES "System Libraries & Requirements"

    Make shure, that the following libraries are in @{b}`LIBS:'@{ub}

            @{fg highlight}*   LIBS:CanDo.library  (Version 3.0 or higher)
            **  LIBS:amigaguide.library  (Version 34.3 or higher)
            **  LIBS:asl.library  (Version 37.4 or higher)
            **  LIBS:datatype.library  (Version 39.4 or higher)@{fg text}

@{b}*   CanDo.library, CanDoGFX.library, InovaMusic.Library@{ub}
    (c) Copyright 1989-95 Inovatronics Inc. All Rights Reserved.

@{b}**  AmigaGuide.library, ASL.Library, DataType.Library@{ub}
    (c) Copyright 1985-2000 Amiga International, All Rights Reserved.

    SyntaxChecker is written to use it with tidy from 26-Jul-1999 or later.

    Make shure, that tidy is at @{b}c:@{ub} or @{b}PROGDIR:@{ub} or
    use a @{" ToolType " link TOOLTYPES} or @{" CLI-Argument " link ARGUMENTS}.

@endnode

